{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "bd9820e7-0d36-47f0-a938-d11b5970de21",
    "name": "Eagle Bank API",
    "description": "This Postman collection provides a complete end-to-end test suite for the Eagle Bank REST API.\n\nIt includes all core banking operations such as user management, authentication, account management, and financial transactions (deposits and withdrawals).\n\nThe API is designed to simulate a real-world banking system with proper security (JWT authentication), role-based access control, and strict ownership rules to ensure users can only access their own data.\n\n\\## Features covered in this collection:\n\n\\- User registration and authentication (JWT-based login)  \n\\- Secure access to protected endpoints using Bearer tokens  \n\\- Full operations for Users  \n\\- Bank Account creation, retrieval, update, and deletion  \n\\- Transaction handling (Deposit & Withdrawal)  \n\\- Transaction history retrieval (read-only audit log)\n\n\\## How authentication works:\n\n1\\. Create User  \n2\\. Use the \"Login\" request to authenticate a user  \n3\\. A JWT token is automatically saved to the environment variable \\`token\\`  \n4\\. All protected endpoints use this token via:  \nAuthorization: Bearer {{token}}\n\n\\## Environment variables used:\n\n\\- baseUrl → API base URL (e.g. [http://localhost:8080](http://localhost:8080))  \n\\- token → JWT authentication token  \n\\- userId → dynamically stored user ID  \n\\- accountId → dynamically stored account ID  \n\\- transactionId → dynamically stored transaction ID\n\n\\## Notes:\n\n\\- Transactions are immutable once created (cannot be updated or deleted)  \n\\- Users can only access and modify their own accounts and data  \n\\- Proper HTTP status codes are used for error handling (400, 401, 403, 404, 422)\n\nThis collection is designed for development, testing, and demonstration purposes and reflects a production-style API structure.",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "_exporter_id": "54635966",
    "_collection_link": "https://go.postman.co/collection/54635966-bd9820e7-0d36-47f0-a938-d11b5970de21?source=collection_link"
  },
